description: Storm your way through three unique worlds, beat each stage, and destroy the bosses! Featuring an original electronic soundtrack, multiple play modes, stages, ships and weapons. Lost Wing is a perfect challenge for the most demanding players.
name: Lost Wing
intro: Pilot a super fast ship through brutal environments, and try to top the leaderboards! Featuring numerous challenges, ships and enemies, Lost Wing is a shot of pure unadulterated adrenaline.
